member.name: M:MyMath.Matrix.Divide(System.Int32[0:,0:],System.Int32)
member.summary: Divides all elements of a matrix by a specified number.
member.param: The number to divide each element by.
member.returns: A new matrix containing the divided elements.
member.remarks: If num is 0, prints "Num cannot be 0" and returns null. If matrix is null, returns null.
